2
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:21,160
Fei Yufei

3
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,520
Isn't this my dear brother?

4
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:44,320
Ding Doudou

5
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:50,920
Xiao Wei

6
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,360
Ding Binbin

7
00:00:55,360 --> 00:00:56,840
Ding Binbin, Wu Liting

8
00:00:58,160 --> 00:01:00,160
Jin Xueyu

9
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:02,290
Jin Xueyu, Liu Mengjunyu, Liu Hongfei

10
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:06,360
Tang Mengjia, Dai Gaozheng, Cheng Yufeng

11
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,480
Zhang Yuehua

12
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:21,360
Liang Jingyu

13
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,570
Song Huainan, you are out of your mind!

14
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,120
So what if I am?

15
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,280
Neither of you will escape today.

16
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,160
Huainan, what are you doing?

17
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,360
He is your brother!

18
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,920
Did he ever treat me as a brother?

19
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,759
He doesn't deserve to be my brother.

20
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,920
Fine. I will kill you right now.

21
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,760
How did you become like this?

22
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,840
It is all thanks to you.

23
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,880
You killed my mother for that bitch.

24
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,320
I'm telling you, this grudge,

25
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:36,010
I will never forget it as long as I live.

26
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,200
I already explained it to you.

27
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,560
It was a misunderstanding. A misunderstanding!

28
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,840
Lies! It is all lies!

29
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,800
At a time like this,

30
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,840
would I still lie to you?

31
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,880
Why can't you understand?

32
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,680
They can all forgive you.

33
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:21,000
I must avenge my father today.

34
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,880
Our Song family wronged your Zhu family.

35
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,840
Take my old life as repayment.

36
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,160
You have committed many crimes. You cannot escape death.

37
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,440
Just surrender.

38
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,200
Why not take my life?

39
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:29,160
Song Qingzhou is appointed as the Military Governor of Jiangcheng.

40
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,660
Let me show you around.

41
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,680
I've dismissed everyone in the Song family.

42
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,200
I also set Yuemei free.

43
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:19,080
There will be no Song family from now on.

44
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,260
Do you want to join our Zhu family?

